0,520],"id":"aaa21dd9-b9c6-6089-87c0-bf3ad5094272","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fetch Changes Since Watermark · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"b9671580-6c12-8998-0b0c-f3f553e070a1","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Changes Since Watermark\n\nGET https://api.example.com/v1/jobs — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Normalize Records · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"0d3c5ec1-59c6-40cc-1b58-aabbd9e3a393","name":"Note: Fetch Changes Since Watermark"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Normalize Records\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming job records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"d989553c-98e5-24cd-654e-b5d9d7cc635b","name":"Note: Normalize Records"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per job (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"301914a6-6942-3b82-a468-11420faed12d","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Upsert into Google Sheets","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"9f57021e-553c-30d2-6195-3c09a54089aa","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Advance Watermark · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"29d14fb3-c57c-c011-2a4e-442628f0466f","name":"Note: Upsert into Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Advance Watermark\n\nCustom JavaScript: Advance the incremental watermark to the newest record seen\n\nNext: Persist Watermark (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,520],"id":"aed4efcc-762b-aa90-4523-1a52f4dacae5","name":"Note: Advance Watermark"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Watermark (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Row Counts Match? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"cc9d6a18-5206-7b6d-c41b-b06aebe9f7b2","name":"Note: Persist Watermark (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Row Counts Match?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.processed >= 0 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Raise Drift Alarm","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"d89e3249-b806-9b5e-358f-b5ca9e718dc3","name":"Note: Row Counts Match?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Raise Drift Alarm\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,970],"id":"f9599160-200a-cfe8-2d97-298eb7ade130","name":"Note: Raise Drift Alarm"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"d2eaf259-a8a9-5528-d320-dfd963add7da","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"e8dda03f-f732-e696-7d9a-89d4e8c7470f","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"38575ac7-937f-efdd-7ede-ac1a7999f5ee","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot 2","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"b2b2b1bb-1c74-fdf9-24f1-8fe02b1d037c","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot 2\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"1836846d-4825-d8bd-0875-d7fb89d5f933","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"b3a2441f-4de0-f41d-782a-88ab5a6db2e2","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"a5c74851-1e5d-782a-3fd3-7757c693fd6c","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"38b7d6c6-a32e-b2a4-ff30-9f6d4e901f22","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Copy to Google Drive","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"e8875c0c-dd96-032a-a237-172516888ffb","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Copy to Google Drive\n\ngoogleDrive — `upload` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Tag Pipeline Metadata · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"b13fc272-6c74-c9d0-3e4b-f4ac1168ab78","name":"Note: Archive Copy to Google Drive"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"540ebd7c-7918-66c5-3839-f78d34e05000","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 25 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Sort Jobs Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"28d2f082-5d52-a0ac-c60b-adc7e56fcd09","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Jobs Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty type","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"dcadb325-fb1d-0c25-988e-b63c1fa751d2","name":"Note: Sort Jobs Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty type\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"5680f233-d1c9-c076-59f3-7504afa83a15","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7770,520],"id":"e37207bd-1b54-dada-06c8-5f083bf57496","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,520],"id":"6d1ba6e8-d780-7f88-ab64-0cfe484940d3","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Telegram · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,520],"id":"e030fa28-5fcf-35bc-6a79-8296a047b47d","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Telegram\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,520],"id":"b88da57c-d4ba-fe0c-7f6e-a683f5f6a5a0","name":"Note: Send Summary to Telegram"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8094,1540],"id":"f23ecedd-c779-64a0-8a29-9802896b8d06","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8418,1540],"id":"da107af4-2418-56b6-ef10-eda4d5c86b05","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8742,1540],"id":"a6d49d2b-8d29-ab74-7127-6c728f5e1cf2","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Automate a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive end to end\n\n**Pattern:** Workflow Automation · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nAutomate a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive end to end. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual triggers is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Load Previous Snapshot → Fetch Changes Since Watermark → Normalize Records → Fingerprint for Idempotency → Drop Already-Processed Items → Upsert into Google Sheets → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to workflow automation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating triggers in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Improves response time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"5968c036-cef2-5f00-48fa-e6aec78e7d17","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"bfbab98f-d48f-5f75-67dc-e0adace193a8","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"c57e12f8-183c-0b74-4616-8d0fc055dc02","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your triggers process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"78e4c6f6-de40-72ac-da50-6db1570337e4","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Changes Since Watermark","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Changes Since Watermark":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Records","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Records":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Advance Watermark","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Advance Watermark":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Watermark (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Watermark (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Row Counts Match?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Row Counts Match?":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Raise Drift Alarm","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot 2","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Copy to Google Drive","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Copy to Google Drive":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Jobs Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Jobs Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty type":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Telegram","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Raise Drift Alarm":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Telegram":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"e5c9033f-4e42-481a-ab33-3294bdf7b721","id":"FDX06360"}